title: Air Fryer Chicken Nuggets
instructions: Preheat air fryer to 400F for 8 minutes. Spray a baking sheet with olive oil spray.Put the olive oil in one bowl and the breadcrumbs, panko and parmesan cheese in another.Season chicken with salt and pepper, then put in the bowl with the olive oil and mix well so the olive oil evenly coats all of the chicken.Put a few chunks of chicken at a time into the breadcrumb mixture to coat, then on the baking sheet.Lightly spray the top with olive oil spray then airfry 8 minutes, turning halfway. Until golden.
